{"sn2.12:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.12 ","sn2.12:0.2":"2. Anathapindikavagga ","sn2.12:0.3":"Vendusutta ","sn2.12:1.1":"Ekamantam thito kho vendu devaputto bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn2.12:2.1":"“Sukhitava te manuja, ","sn2.12:2.2":"sugatam payirupasiya; ","sn2.12:2.3":"Yunjam gotamasasane, ","sn2.12:2.4":"appamatta nu sikkhare”ti. ","sn2.12:3.1":"“Ye me pavutte sitthipade, ","sn2.12:3.2":"(venduti bhagava) ","sn2.12:3.3":"Anusikkhanti jhayino; ","sn2.12:3.4":"Kale te appamajjanta, ","sn2.12:3.5":"Na maccuvasaga siyun”ti. "}